se.miun.itm.input.sql.example

Class FilesToDatabaseTransferrer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.miun.itm.input.sql.example.FilesToDatabaseTransferrer<T>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExperimentArchivesToDatabaseTransferrer, XMLFilesToDatabaseTransferrer

    public abstract class FilesToDatabaseTransferrer<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract base class for classes that transfers objects from files to SQL databases and displays a frame with information about the progress.
    Author:
    Stefan Karlsson
